data.name: lblWeAreWilson.Text
data.value: At Wilson Sporting Goods, we are a leading manufacturer of sports equipment based in Chicago, Illinois. Our company was founded in 1913 and has become a trusted and respected name in the sporting goods industry, offering a wide range of products for various sports including tennis, baseball, football, basketball, golf, and volleyball.

data.name: lblWilsonInfo2.Text
data.value: Our tennis rackets are used by professional players around the world, while our footballs are used by the National Football League (NFL) and our baseball gloves are used by Major League Baseball (MLB) players. We are also proud sponsors of numerous professional athletes and sports teams, further solidifying our reputation as a top-tier sporting goods manufacturer.
